title: Existing Reports
text: Correct: Existing reports can help you with your baseline understanding of the project you are trying to tackle

title: The database
text: Incorrect: Although you will use the database or source data, it is typically not the first place you want to start

title: Technical Documentation
text: Incorrect: Technical documentation is handy and valuable, but to get the most from the documentation, it's helpful to understand more about something else being used at an organization

title: Queries
text: Incorrect: As an analyst you will be writing queries, but at the outset of any project, looking at the queries that have been developed already can give you a faster start
